<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.5.8">
<l>poṉmuṭiyam pōrēṟṟai yemmāṉai nāṭaṭantō</l>
<l>ṭaṉmuṭivoṉ ṟillāta taṇṭuḻāy mālaiyaṉai</l>
<l>yeṉmuṭivu kāṇātē yeṉṉuḷ kalantāṉaic</l>
<l>coṉmuṭivu kāṇēṉāṉ colluvateṉ collīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>About the battle bull with a gold crown, our lord, the one with a garland</l>
<l>of cool Tulsi without any limit to [his] four large arms,</l>
<l>the one who mingled with my heart without seeing my limitations,</l>
<l>I don’t see a limit of words; what shall I say, tell [me]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
